Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.28,0:00:14.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you really grant any wish?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.53,0:00:18.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. I can grant your wish, no problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.86,0:00:22.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, is that what you really want?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.20,0:00:24.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.91,0:00:48.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.14,0:00:50.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.57,0:00:53.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is your destiny.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.85,0:02:48.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.48,0:02:50.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pardon me. {she speaks this in a formal manner}{gee, thanks}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.11,0:02:52.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Hitomi? Didn't sleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.60,0:02:57.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The police kept me at the hospital late last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.06,0:02:59.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.10,0:03:02.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems as though I was sleep-walking or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.34,0:03:09.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There were some other girls there, but they were all out cold when I woke up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.04,0:03:10.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.75,0:03:14.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The doctor said it could have been a collective hallucination.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.68,0:03:18.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He wants me to come back in for more testing after school.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.91,0:03:21.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's such a bother.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.53,0:03:24.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't you just stay home today, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.51,0:03:25.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.92,0:03:31.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,People would think that I'm really sick, and my family would be worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.46,0:03:35.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's our honor student! You're so mature!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.61,0:03:48.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't felt this good in ages!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.04,0:03:50.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is great!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.81,0:03:53.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, Sayaka-chan. Aren't you scared?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.96,0:04:00.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm? Well, of course I'm a little scared. But that went pretty well yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.55,0:04:10.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I had to say it, I'm more afraid of losing you and Hitomi. You two are my best friends, after all. {something missing here? -masat}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.06,0:04:12.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.18,0:04:21.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How should I put it? Confident? Clear-minded? It's like I can trust myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.40,0:04:25.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever the case, I feel great!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.91,0:04:33.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mitakihara will now be under the protection of the great Magical Girl Sayaka-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.55,0:04:36.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't regret it at all?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.90,0:04:39.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.58,0:04:41.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I were to regret anything,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.80,0:04:44.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it would be that I hesitated.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.56,0:04:49.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder how things would be if I had chosen sooner.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.20,0:04:57.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we had both fought at that time, Mami-san may have lived.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.49,0:05:00.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.71,0:05:13.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You need to stop thinking like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.37,0:05:16.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.18,0:05:19.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just saying this because you can't change the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.59,0:05:26.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't really explain it even if I try. I just wanted to become a Magical Girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.49,0:05:28.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sayaka-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.45,0:05:32.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I found my wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.73,0:05:38.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's something that I'm willing to risk my life for.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.36,0:05:43.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my fault for not realizing it until now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.12,0:05:50.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you shouldn't feel bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.23,0:05:56.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It just means that you don't have to become a Magical Girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.84,0:06:03.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I've got to get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.51,0:06:05.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? You have plans?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.78,0:06:07.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.89,0:06:13.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. So you can't leave yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.92,0:06:20.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I still have some therapy. They won't let me leave until I can walk again.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.40,0:06:26.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As for my hand, they have no idea why it suddenly got better.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.68,0:06:30.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They'd like to keep it under observation for a little longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.08,0:06:37.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How are you feeling? Are you still in any pain?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.68,0:06:45.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,None at all. That's what surprises me the most. It's like the accident was just a bad dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.06,0:06:48.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't even know what I'm doing in this bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.51,0:06:53.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's like you said. This is a miracle, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.84,0:06:58.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.94,0:07:04.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I said some pretty horrible things to you, Sayaka-chan. I'm not sure what got into me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.82,0:07:07.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no need to remember things like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.52,0:07:12.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All that matters is that you're happy now. Don't make such a sad face.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.33,0:07:15.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I felt like I was running out of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.83,0:07:18.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, don't overdo it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.75,0:07:21.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, look at the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.26,0:07:27.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyousuke, why don't we get some fresh air?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.34,0:07:30.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's on the roof?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.06,0:07:31.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.61,0:07:54.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.40,0:07:57.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The real celebration{TLC Note: "celebration, congratulations"} doesn't come until you're officially discharged,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.52,0:07:59.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but we decided to do something to celebrate your recovery first.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.84,0:08:01.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.64,0:08:07.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You asked me to get rid of it, but I just couldn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.14,0:08:10.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.65,0:08:28.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go on. There's nothing to be scared of.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.86,0:09:11.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mami,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.19,0:09:15.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,my wish has finally come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.70,0:09:19.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How could I regret it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.95,0:09:25.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never been this happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.54,0:09:54.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.64,0:10:00.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's the new Magical Girl in town.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.12,0:10:04.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you really intending on fighting her?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.38,0:10:05.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's obviously a pushover.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.88,0:10:10.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd finish her off in an instant. Who cares?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.46,0:10:14.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You got a problem with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.72,0:10:18.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It may not be as easy as you think.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.13,0:10:21.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, she's not the only other Magical Girl here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.48,0:10:24.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? And who would that be?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.73,0:10:27.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.23,0:10:33.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Didn't she make a contract with you to become a Magical Girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.24,0:10:35.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You could say that she both did and didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.99,0:10:39.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's a peculiar one.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.54,0:10:43.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even I don't know what she'll do.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.75,0:10:47.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This makes things more interesting. I was worried that I was going to get bored.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.35,0:10:50.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe it'll even be fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.80,0:11:01.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you want to talk about?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.08,0:11:07.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's about Sayaka-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.59,0:11:16.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's stubborn, she gets nervous easily, and she's always getting into fights.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.48,0:11:18.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But she's a good girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.86,0:11:23.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's kind, bold, and she always tries her best to help others.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.51,0:11:26.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As a Magical Girl, that's a fatal flaw.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.50,0:11:28.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that... so...?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.85,0:11:34.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kindness begets naivety. Courage begets imprudence. {TLC Note:  "Kindness comes with naivety, courage becomes imrpudence."}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.84,0:11:38.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no reward for devotion.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.41,0:11:43.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those who can't understand that are not fit to be Magical Girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.93,0:11:46.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why Tomoe Mami lost her life.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.14,0:11:51.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say that!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.10,0:11:58.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sayaka-chan says that she's fine...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.08,0:12:05.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...but I don't want what happened to Mami to happen to her as well. What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.03,0:12:08.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're worried about Miki Sayaka, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.01,0:12:14.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing I can do for her, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.95,0:12:17.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So please, Homura-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.19,0:12:23.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be friends with Sayaka-chan and don't fight with her, like how things were with you and Mami.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.74,0:12:29.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be much safer if you go after the Witches together rather than going alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.79,0:12:41.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to make any false promises.{missing line here? TLC -masat}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.11,0:12:46.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I suggest you give up on Miki Sayaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.35,0:12:53.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.17,0:12:56.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She didn't have to make a contract.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.19,0:13:02.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was my mistake. I should have protected her, as I had you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.50,0:13:04.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.15,0:13:11.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll accept the responsibility, as this is an irreversible mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.93,0:13:14.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Similar to the way one can't be brought back from the dead,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.99,0:13:21.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,there's no saving someone once they've become a Magical Girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.44,0:13:28.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Making the contract means giving up everything you have for that one wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.17,0:13:33.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you've given up...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.11,0:13:36.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...on yourself and all those other girls?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.53,0:13:38.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.57,0:13:42.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't ask for your forgiveness.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.31,0:13:46.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Regardless how heavy my sins may be, I must continue to fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.22,0:13:56.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like I've wasted your time. Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.37,0:14:14.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you nervous?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.33,0:14:18.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Naturally. One mistake and it's game over.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.71,0:14:23.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Madoka?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.97,0:14:27.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sayaka-chan, are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.30,0:14:32.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep! I'm going out on patrol in search of Witches. It's my duty as an ally of justice!{TLC Note: "Ally of Justice"}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.74,0:14:36.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay going alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.35,0:14:42.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course. That's how Mami-san did it. I'm her student too, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.11,0:14:48.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uhm... I won't be of much help, and I'd probably just get in the way...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.14,0:14:56.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...but I promise I won't be a nuisance if you let me come with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.84,0:15:01.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you trying too hard?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.38,0:15:03.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm... sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.15,0:15:06.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right. I'd definitely just get in the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.89,0:15:09.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all. It'd make me really happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.12,0:15:16.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My hands haven't stopped shaking for a while now. Can you tell?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.26,0:15:22.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's kinda lame as a Magical Girl, but I feel lonely going on my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.27,0:15:23.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sayaka-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.95,0:15:26.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You won't be a nuisance. I'm really happy you want to come.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.87,0:15:33.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel calmer when I've got someone with me, like I can do anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.21,0:15:34.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.47,0:15:39.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll protect you! Come on, you'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.07,0:15:42.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's hunt Witches like we did before.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.33,0:15:46.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You understand the dangers, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.80,0:15:52.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know I'm clumsy so I'm bound to make mistakes on my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.28,0:15:56.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if Madoka's with me, I'll be more careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.96,0:15:58.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.12,0:16:01.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine as long as you understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.34,0:16:02.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyubei...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.58,0:16:07.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have your reasons too, Madoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.96,0:16:11.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know you want to protect Sayaka-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.32,0:16:17.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as you're there to support Sayaka, there's no limit to what you can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.85,0:16:21.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.68,0:16:24.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't need to say anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.82,0:16:26.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure Sayaka-chan would agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.23,0:16:34.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you make the decision, I'll be ready to grant your wish anytime.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.89,0:16:48.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.94,0:16:54.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This barrier must have been set up by a familiar instead of a Witch.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.67,0:16:58.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get cocky. You're still new at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.66,0:17:00.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be sloppy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.55,0:17:02.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.05,0:17:13.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.06,0:17:13.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's getting away!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.81,0:17:14.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got this!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.72,0:17:46.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait up. What do you two think you're doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.92,0:17:50.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's getting away!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.34,0:17:56.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you tell by looking? That wasn't a Witch, only a familiar.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.33,0:17:58.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They don't even carry grief seeds.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.59,0:18:02.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if we don't do something about it, someone could be killed!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.88,0:18:09.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should just wait for it to kill someone so that it'll become a Witch.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.90,0:18:13.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then you can get grief seeds from it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.80,0:18:17.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think will happen to your chicken if you break the egg?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.32,0:18:22.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you saying we should just stand around while it kills people?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.93,0:18:27.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You sure are weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.82,0:18:31.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you know? They should have taught you all about the food chain in school.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.46,0:18:37.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Witches eat weak humans, and we eat them.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.22,0:18:43.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's nature's law. This is how we separate the weak from the strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.97,0:18:46.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.27,0:18:49.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.48,0:18:56.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me you believe in "helping people" and "justice".
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.39,0:19:01.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that the real reason you made that contract with this little guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.55,0:19:03.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say whatever you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.91,0:19:12.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you just give up?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.46,0:19:26.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Joining us for some half-assed reason...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.73,0:19:28.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're pissing me off.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.57,0:19:37.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sayaka-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.90,0:19:43.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmph. Why don't you cool your head a bit?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.15,0:19:53.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's strange. That attack should have had you out of commission for three months.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.88,0:19:56.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sayaka-chan, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.35,0:20:00.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because she became a Magical Girl by wishing for someone's health...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.97,0:20:03.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...her regenerative powers are amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.29,0:20:07.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who the hell would listen to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.45,0:20:11.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it weren't for people like you, Mami-san wouldn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.62,0:20:12.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're annoying.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.85,0:20:15.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Very annoying!{loldicks}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.48,0:20:23.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's your problem? You shouldn't talk to your seniors like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.49,0:20:25.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.28,0:20:32.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who do you think you're talking to?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.79,0:20:37.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sayaka-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.72,0:20:39.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Madoka, stay back! It's dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.43,0:20:48.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a fool who understands neither words nor beatings.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.18,0:20:52.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like I have no choice but to kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.94,0:21:01.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.45,0:21:06.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like hell I'd lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.29,0:21:22.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why? Hey, why is this happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.91,0:21:27.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do we have to fight each other even when there are no Witches?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.66,0:21:31.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing I can do. Neither of them will back down.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.52,0:21:37.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyubei, please make them stop. This isn't right!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.91,0:21:40.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing I can do, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.35,0:21:45.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want them to stop, there is a way.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.70,0:21:51.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Only another Magical Girl can interfere.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.85,0:21:55.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have the ability to choose that if that is what you wish for.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.71,0:21:59.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. If I make a contract...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.86,0:22:05.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.99,0:22:12.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.18,0:22:13.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That won't be necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.47,0:24:11.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sayaka-chan, you became a Magical Girl to go after Witches, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.54,0:24:15.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's not a Witch, she's a Magical Girl like you...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.13,0:24:19.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is very strange.
